    <item>
      <title>Overview</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/docs/guides/landing-page/overview/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 19:49:34 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/docs/guides/landing-page/overview/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The Lotus Docs theme features a built-in landing page that&amp;rsquo;s easy to customise and manage.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;text-center&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/lotusdocs_screenshot_2023-11-16_at_19-59-06_btprao_8571235238308548821.webp&#34; alt=&#34;Landing Page Screenshot&#34; width=&#34;802&#34; height=&#34;1214&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;  &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The landing page layout is comprised of individual sections, each with their own &lt;a data-bs-delay=&#34;{&amp;#34;hide&amp;#34;:300,&amp;#34;show&amp;#34;:550}&#34; data-bs-html=&#34;true&#34; data-bs-title=&#34;&lt;a href=&#39;//localhost:1313/docs/guides/landing-page/templates/&#39;&gt;&lt;p&gt;LANDING PAGE&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Templates&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;A guide to using the Lotus Docs landing page templates.&lt;/a&gt;&#34; data-bs-toggle=&#34;tooltip&#34; href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/guides/landing-page/templates/&#34;&gt;template&lt;/a&gt;. These sections are configured via a &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/templates/data-templates/#data-files-in-themes&#34; rel=&#34;external&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;data file&lt;svg width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; d=&#34;M14 5c-.552 0-1-.448-1-1s.448-1 1-1h6c.552 0 1 .448 1 1v6c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1v-3.586l-7.293 7.293c-.391.39-1.024.39-1.414 0-.391-.391-.391-1.024 0-1.414l7.293-7.293h-3.586zm-9 2c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v11c0 .552.448 1 1 1h11c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-4.563c0-.552.448-1 1-1s1 .448 1 1v4.563c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3h-11c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3v-11c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3h4.563c.552 0 1 .448 1 1s-.448 1-1 1h-4.563z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; named &lt;code&gt;landing.yaml&lt;/code&gt; in your &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/templates/data-templates/#the-data-directory&#34; rel=&#34;external&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;/data&lt;/code&gt; directory.&lt;svg width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; d=&#34;M14 5c-.552 0-1-.448-1-1s.448-1 1-1h6c.552 0 1 .448 1 1v6c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1v-3.586l-7.293 7.293c-.391.39-1.024.39-1.414 0-.391-.391-.391-1.024 0-1.414l7.293-7.293h-3.586zm-9 2c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v11c0 .552.448 1 1 1h11c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-4.563c0-.552.448-1 1-1s1 .448 1 1v4.563c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3h-11c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3v-11c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3h4.563c.552 0 1 .448 1 1s-.448 1-1 1h-4.563z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Templates</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/docs/guides/landing-page/templates/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Dec 2022 19:19:31 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/docs/guides/landing-page/templates/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction&#34;&gt;Introduction &lt;a href=&#34;#introduction&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;material-icons align-middle&#34;&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each section on the landing page corresponds to a specific template with its own set of parameters for customisation. There are (currently) 4 templates.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;table class=&#34;table table table-striped&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Name&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Type&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/guides/landing-page/templates/#hero&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;hero&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;hero&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;A basic hero template with text and CTA buttons on the left and an image on the right. Traditionally the first section of a landing page.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/guides/landing-page/templates/#feature-grid&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;feature grid&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;grid&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;A multi row, 3 column grid listing features. Each feature consists of an icon, title, and descriptive text.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/guides/landing-page/templates/#image-text&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;image text&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;image + text&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;A 2 column section with an image on the left (or the right) with some descriptive text, lists and a call-to-action button adjacent.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/guides/landing-page/templates/#image-compare&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;image compare&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;image comparison&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Utilizes the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/kylewetton/image-compare-viewer&#34; rel=&#34;external&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;image-compare-viewer&lt;svg width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; d=&#34;M14 5c-.552 0-1-.448-1-1s.448-1 1-1h6c.552 0 1 .448 1 1v6c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1v-3.586l-7.293 7.293c-.391.39-1.024.39-1.414 0-.391-.391-.391-1.024 0-1.414l7.293-7.293h-3.586zm-9 2c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v11c0 .552.448 1 1 1h11c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-4.563c0-.552.448-1 1-1s1 .448 1 1v4.563c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3h-11c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3v-11c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3h4.563c.552 0 1 .448 1 1s-.448 1-1 1h-4.563z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; library by &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/kylewetton&#34; rel=&#34;external&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Kyle Wetton&lt;svg width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; d=&#34;M14 5c-.552 0-1-.448-1-1s.448-1 1-1h6c.552 0 1 .448 1 1v6c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1v-3.586l-7.293 7.293c-.391.39-1.024.39-1.414 0-.391-.391-.391-1.024 0-1.414l7.293-7.293h-3.586zm-9 2c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v11c0 .552.448 1 1 1h11c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-4.563c0-.552.448-1 1-1s1 .448 1 1v4.563c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3h-11c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3v-11c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3h4.563c.552 0 1 .448 1 1s-.448 1-1 1h-4.563z&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to compare multiple before and after images. Includes an auto-generated tab to switch between image comparison sets.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;alert alert-default d-flex&#34; role=&#34;alert&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;flex-shrink-1 alert-icon&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;material-icons size-20 me-2&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  notifications&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34;&gt;Additional templates and template types are part of the Lotus Docs roadmap&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;required-data-file-parameters&#34;&gt;Required data file parameters &lt;a href=&#34;#required-data-file-parameters&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;material-icons align-middle&#34;&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;For each enabled section defined in your data file (&lt;code&gt;/data/landing.yaml&lt;/code&gt;), the following parameters are required:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
